This is a list of reproducible bugs that have affected some version of !tabby

Test #1

Add two !SrcEdit windows and detatch the first one.

Test #2

Add a !SrcEdit window and then two !Draw windows.  Then quit !Draw.

Test #3

Add a !WinEd window from a saved template.

Test #4

Add a !WinEd window from a saved template and check that the size of the
window can be adjusted correctly.

Test #5 

Open a new !tabby instance and click adjust/menu on the empty tab bar